            title: "Why the Everyday Name Bib is Machine-Embroidered and the Heritage Pieces Are Hand-Stitched",
            excerpt: "Both are old crafts, chosen for different reasons. Here's what each one is good for — and why the everyday name bib and the heritage cross-stitched pieces are made by different methods on purpose.",
            publishedAt: "2026-05-17",
            readMinutes: 4,
