                .p("Cross-stitch and embroidery aren't the same thing, even though most people use the words interchangeably."),
                .p("Embroidery is a broad family of techniques — satin stitch, French knots, chain stitch, machine embroidery — basically any way of decorating fabric with thread. Cross-stitch is one specific technique within that family, but it's old enough and exacting enough to deserve its own name."),
